        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[想跑步，但小腿会变粗[裂开]不会！🙅🏻跑步后发现小腿和大腿变粗，是因为锻炼后腿部充血，导致肌肉看上去“膨胀”了！最多十几个小时就会减小到原来状态。[...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[想跑步，但小腿会变粗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>不会！🙅🏻<br><br>跑步后发现小腿和大腿变粗，是因为锻炼后腿部充血，导致肌肉看上去“膨胀”了！最多十几个小时就会减小到原来状态。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>卫子建议，在跑步后，及时放松、拉伸双腿，这样可以帮助肌肉更快恢复！（别再给懒找借口了<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（央视新闻）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjden1xbr9g20dw0c6qer.gif" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
