            <title><![CDATA[【[并不简单]#牛皮癣其实并不会传染#】银屑病，俗称“牛皮癣”。在我国，有650多万人被银屑病困扰。[话筒]医生介绍，牛皮癣的“癣”与足癣等不同，它不是真菌感...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[并不简单]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_bingbujiandan-9955880b30.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E7%89%9B%E7%9A%AE%E7%99%A3%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%23&amp;extparam=%23%E7%89%9B%E7%9A%AE%E7%99%A3%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E5%B9%B6%E4%B8%8D%E4%BC%9A%E4%BC%A0%E6%9F%93%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#牛皮癣其实并不会传染#</span></a>】银屑病，俗称“牛皮癣”。在我国，有650多万人被银屑病困扰。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生介绍，牛皮癣的“癣”与足癣等不同，它不是真菌感染，而是与自身免疫相关的炎症，不会传染。此外，银屑病尚无法根治切勿盲信偏方，患者需要通过规范合理的治疗，对病情进行有效控制。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4962106005454885" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hjbv59mjg5j60po0y84nt02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/EenQUvPZlx089Ko89Rdm01041200oDYy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1698728523&amp;ssig=iFHzNdbf%2Bs&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/fpily1dHlx089Ko8NGiY01041200ebrL0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1698728523&amp;ssig=SmTVm4tzd8&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/s21zXoL1lx089Ko8zbPG010412007nWo0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1698728523&amp;ssig=LRnfQ2TJlu&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4962106005454885" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
