            <description><![CDATA[【“恐矮”爸妈抢着打的生长激素，我也能给娃“来一针”吗<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[可怜]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_kelian-a9df4278bf.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】我家孩子怎么全班最矮？孩子挑食会不会长不高？打个生长激素“拔高”吧？这种身高焦虑，很多父母身上都有，但卫子想说，生长激素可不是想打就能打的。先别慌！咱得了解影响孩子“身高”的原因才能对症下药，再盘点几个关于身高的误区，收好不谢<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（四川大学华西医院）<img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjd2pgvstgj20u019rjy2.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjd2phpkwkj20u01smn68.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjd2phwvnwj20u01sk116.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjd2piay4rj20u01skwnl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjd2pio6e8j20u02b6na5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hjd2phz0h3j20u01cjwlh.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
